## Example

```nocap
lowkey greet(name: text) -> text {
    comeback "Yo, " + name + "! ðŸ‘‹"
}

fr names: lineup<text> = ["Alice", "Bob", "Charlie"]
each person in names {
    yap(greet(person))
}
```

